WITH fb_data as (
  WITH column1 as ($fbcolumn1),
  column2 as ($fbcolumn2),
  column3 as (
    WITH post_interactions AS (
      SELECT
        profileID,
        sum(
          IFNULL(
            post_reactions_by_type_total_like + post_reactions_by_type_total_love + post_reactions_by_type_total_wow + post_reactions_by_type_total_haha + post_reactions_by_type_total_sorry + post_reactions_by_type_total_anger,
            0
          ) + IFNULL(post_activity_by_action_type_comment, 0) + IFNULL(post_activity_by_action_type_share, 0)
        ) as interactions
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly${dataset_suffix}.facebookInsightsOwnPosts${table_suffix}`
      WHERE
        $LRA_condition
        AND $Condition
      GROUP BY
        profileID
    ),
    num_posts AS (
      SELECT
        profileID,
        IFNULL(COUNT(DISTINCT externalID), 0) as posts
      FROM
        `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly${dataset_suffix}.facebookInsightsOwnPosts${table_suffix}`
      WHERE
        $LRA_condition
        AND $Condition
      GROUP BY
        profileID
    )
    SELECT
      A.profileID as profileID,
      IFNULL(
        SAFE_DIVIDE(IFNULL(interactions, 0), (IFNULL(posts, 0))),
        0
      ) as column3_summe
    FROM
      post_interactions A FULL
      JOIN num_posts B ON A.profileID = B.profileID
  ),
  column4 as ($fbcolumn4)
  SELECT
    column1_summe,
    column2_summe,
    column3_summe,
    column4_summe,
    column1.profileID as profileID
  FROM
    column1
    JOIN column2 ON column1.profileID = column2.profileID
    JOIN column3 ON column2.profileID = column3.profileID
    JOIN column4 ON column3.profileID = column4.profileID
    JOIN `ndr-code-bi-dashboard.Quintly.profiles` Q ON column1.profileID = Q.facebookID
  WHERE
    profile NOT LIKE "Tagesschau"
    AND Q.LRA = '$LRA'
),
column1_quantile_data AS(
  SELECT
    PERCENTILE_CONT(column1_summe, 0.25) OVER() AS column1_Q1,
    PERCENTILE_CONT(column1_summe, 0.5) OVER() AS column1_Median,
    PERCENTILE_CONT(column1_summe, 0.75) OVER() AS column1_Q3,
    profileId
  FROM
    fb_data
),
categorized_data as (
  SELECT
    column1_summe,
    fb_data.profileId as profileID,
    column2_summe,
    column3_summe,
    column4_summe,
    CASE
      WHEN column1_summe < column1_Q1 THEN 'Low'
      WHEN column1_summe >= column1_Q1
      AND column1_summe < column1_Median THEN 'Zwischen dem 1. Quartil und Median'
      WHEN column1_summe >= column1_Median
      AND column1_summe < column1_Q3 THEN 'Zwischen Median und dem 3. Quartil'
      ELSE 'Top'
    END AS order_Kategorie
  FROM
    fb_data
    JOIN column1_quantile_data ON column1_quantile_data.profileID = fb_data.profileID
),
filtered_data as (
  SELECT
    *
  FROM
    categorized_data
  WHERE
    $filterCondition
),

  SELECT
    PERCENTILE_CONT(column1_summe, 0.25) OVER() AS Q1,
    PERCENTILE_CONT(column1_summe, 0.5) OVER() AS Median,
    PERCENTILE_CONT(column1_summe, 0.75) OVER() AS Q3,
    profileId
  FROM
    filtered_data
)
SELECT
